                  </hi>. I am in the employ of James Bassett, a pawn<lb></lb>broker—this jacket was pawned by the prisoner on Tuesday, the 14th of March—I am sure he is the man.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence.</hi> I found the ticket in Sun-street.</p>
